    "body": "The user experience of pull payments is much weaker than that of push payments. \n\nPerhaps something could be done using an external contract as a timer or \"cron job runner\" to initiate the withdrawal for customers after a certain time.\n\nDapps which are intended to hold less value (ex. https://github.com/makoto/blockparty) may also be an acceptable use of push payments.\n",
